name: K M
review: Pastor Ken Golden is very personable and made sure he chatted with me. He suggested we meet for coffee to discuss any questions I had. We will meet today, in fact! The service seems biblical from what I saw online and I will attend an in- person service today. I look forward to meeting with Pastor Golden to discuss this Churches beliefs along with the books he provided!

name: Amanda Hans
review: These people are amazing, knowledgeable, friendly, but most importantly, teach from the Bible.
